item.title: CVE-2019-10392|2024-08-04T22:17:20.645Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20git%20client%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Git Client Plugin 2.8.4 and earlier and 3.0.0-rc did not properly restrict values passed as URL argument to an invocation of 'git ls-remote', resulting in OS command injection.
